GIT is a Technology
GIT-HUB is a platform



	TYPES
LOCA --- within ones Sys
CENTRALIZED --- Collab , but cant be Backup when crashed
DISTRIBUTED --- Collab ,Can be Backup when crashed    -- e.g.. Bitbucket ,Git-Hub



